          "process_md": "&gt; **Teacher applications:**\n\n**Stage-1: Institutional Proposal Submission**\n\n   1. **Proposal Initiative**: College/university takes the initiative to submit a proposal for hosting the STTP program.   1. **Proposal Content**: This proposal outlines the chosen topic, objectives, resource persons, budget, and participant details.   1. **Submission Platform**: The institution submits the proposal online through the AICTE portal.\n&lt;br&gt;\n\n**Stage 2: Individual Teacher Application**\n\n   1. **Proposal Approval**: Once institution&amp;#39;s proposal gets approved, it receives details and guidelines for participant applications.   1. **Application Procedure:** You, as a faculty member interested in participating, can then apply through the institute&amp;#39;s internal mechanism or designated online portal.   1. **Application Requirements**:\n\n\n    - Duly filled application form\n    - Biodata and recent photograph\n    - Curriculum vitae highlighting relevant teaching experience and qualifications\n    - Statement of purpose explaining your interest in the chosen STTP topic\n    - Recommendation letter from the Head of Department or Principal\n\n\n"
        }
